Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:38.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:42.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
